kLoOljfmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOTjhDlkQPDXxxkLoOljfmQ&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=9109016b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OTjhDlkQPDXxxkLoOljfmQ</a><br />\n路面情況請留意大台<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFgtzp9bm2hkIrzYGw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFgtzp9bm2hkIrzYGw&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=102f91dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFgtzp9bm2hkIrzYGw</a>"},{"pid":"9a50be8ca32da8efeee3b2ee824c9ba06359a1b6","tid":1734150,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"講真 今次好撚驚<br />\n但冇得唔出"},{"pid":"77652d782e79196da3d5efe39ece0914bde49c38","tid":1734150,"uid":288182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"係邊"}]}